headline: C3 AI Announces Fiscal First Quarter 2026 Financial Results
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., September 03, 2025--C3.ai, Inc. ("C3 AI," "C3," or the "Company") (NYSE: AI), the Enterprise AI application software company, today announced financial results for its fiscal first quarter ended July 31, 2025. These results are consistent with the preliminary financial results the Company announced on August 8, 2025.

headline: Warren Buffett’s New Stock Bets Revealed — Should You Buy In, Too?
summary: Recently, Warren Buffett’s holding company, Berkshire Hathaway, filed its quarterly Form 13F equity investment portfolio, providing investors with an update regarding the company’s holdings. The filing indicated, among other things, five newer holdings that Buffett and Berkshire have acquired, including one rather surprising investment in a very controversial and embattled company.

headline: Nucor Gains 20% in 3 Months: How Should Investors Play the Stock?
summary: Nucor stock has jumped 20% in three months as growth projects and acquisitions boost momentum despite the recent retreat in steel prices.
